snippet.textDisplay: So many queens on one stage. I was blown away by this performance and I love that they added all the other languages from around the world too. Each woman looked absolutely stunning and their live vocals were just beautiful to hear solo and all together. I love how Disney can bring people from around the world together. That's where the true magic is created. Oh and how can I forget Aurora's voice is so angelic, hearing her in the beginning brought me to tears. I love this song so much and we covered "Into the Unknown" on my channel, hope you will watch it. Bravo ladies. You are true queens.
